1
00:00:00,780 --> 00:00:01,580
Hi everyone!

2
00:00:01,720 --> 00:00:05,920
I want to show an interesting effect, how the Tesla affects the current in the system.

3
00:00:06,780 --> 00:00:10,780
We'll track the current through a current transformer on the inductor's hot end.

4
00:00:11,360 --> 00:00:14,160
Here it is, yellow channel load.

5
00:00:14,260 --> 00:00:15,420
We have a 300W lamp.

6
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:17,400
This will be the consumption.

7
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:18,920
Turning on the push-pull.

8
00:00:20,700 --> 00:00:22,580
Hear the characteristic sound.

9
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,020
OK, consumption.

10
00:00:26,460 --> 00:00:28,180
1.4 A.

11
00:00:28,180 --> 00:00:30,760
This is our current.

12
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,620
Now I'm turning on the Tesla.

13
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:35,600
Interesting moment.

14
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:38,260
Feeding power to the Tesla converter.

15
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:42,180
Current jumped.

16
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:48,040
Adjusting synchronization a bit.

17
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,740
Influence visible.

18
00:00:51,220 --> 00:00:53,800
Bringing hand close to the Tesla.

19
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:57,640
Hissing starts in the pot core.

20
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:01,600
Influence going.

21
00:01:04,670 --> 00:01:08,130
Here clearly visible the Tesla strike location.

22
00:01:08,950 --> 00:01:10,430
No dead time.

23
00:01:12,190 --> 00:01:15,030
Practically maximum current rise moment.

24
00:01:15,870 --> 00:01:17,390
Turning off the Tesla.

25
00:01:18,790 --> 00:01:19,030
That's it.

26
00:01:19,910 --> 00:01:21,190
No current in the circuit.

27
00:01:23,450 --> 00:01:24,750
Starting again.

28
00:01:26,310 --> 00:01:28,870
Can see how much current amplitude.

29
00:01:35,210 --> 00:01:42,350
Practically, at minimum, a doubling occurs.

30
00:01:43,110 --> 00:01:43,850
And that's it.

31
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:45,270
But this isn't the working mode.

32
00:01:45,730 --> 00:01:47,430
Just tuned an interesting moment.

33
00:01:48,550 --> 00:01:50,370
Consumption at the same level.

34
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:53,150
And here look what's happening with the lamp.

35
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:55,690
Now the Tesla isn't quite coordinated.

36
00:01:55,810 --> 00:01:57,590
It's suppressing current at output.

37
00:01:59,290 --> 00:02:00,370
Turning it off.

38
00:02:00,830 --> 00:02:02,470
Bam, lamp lit up.

39
00:02:03,410 --> 00:02:04,290
And consumption.

40
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:06,870
And here I turn it on.

41
00:02:08,350 --> 00:02:09,150
Bam.

42
00:02:10,810 --> 00:02:12,190
Current in circuit grew.

43
00:02:12,350 --> 00:02:13,910
Current at output decreased.

44
00:02:16,050 --> 00:02:18,050
Moment worth attention.

45
00:02:19,610 --> 00:02:21,350
Will work a bit more.

46
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:24,910
And will need to tune the moment when the lamp will light up.
